# My Gym App (Backend)

Description...

### How to set it up

- Download stable version of python (https://www.python.org)
- Create a virtual environment `pipenv shell`
- Install requirements.txt `pip install -r requirements.txt`
- Run the app

### Testing

#### Structure

```
├── app
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── main.py
├── tests
│   ├── unit_tests
│   │   ├── test_main.py
│   ├── integration_tests

```

```
PYTHONPATH=/path/to/project/ pytest tests/unit_tests/test_main.py
```